\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Where were you born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1463222\charrsid12473461 Gospel}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461  Oak. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 What was the name of the road?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 It was Lambeth Street. Lambeth. Lambeth Street. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1463222\charrsid12473461 Gospel}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461  Oak.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 How many years did you live in that house where you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 I was born in 1902 and I lived there 'til I was - when did I leave there - I think - when did we leave there - when David was born. I sh
ould think about 1930. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 So you were born in 1902?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 '02, yes, it must be about 19 - that because my sister was married in there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And you lived in that house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Lived in that house all the time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Until 1930?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 About 1930.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 When you were twenty-eight?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Where did you go to live them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Came over here, Hendon. That's right, yes, we all moved over here together.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 The whole family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 The whole family moved from there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, my father
 had died and my mother had died and then we moved - left there and came over here and bought the house at which stage it had started to be built when we came here and we all came over here together. To Hendon. And then I stopped there 'til - well I've be
en here ever since practically really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Until the end of 1918 you were living in }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1463222\charrsid12473461 Gospel}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461  Oak?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1463222\charrsid12473461 Gospel}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461  Oak, yes, was here during the war.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 How many brothers and sisters did you have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 I had four - four sisters and one brother. Six of us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Can you remember how they came - who's the eldest?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 I'm next the eldest - well about a year and five months between each one, year and say, year and six months between each one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Was the eldest a boy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, they young - next to the youngest.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 The eldest was a girl?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. The eldest was a girl.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And then yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Myself, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And then - I had another sister, she died. Then I had another sister and she died. And then my brother was born and then Peggy w
as born. She's the youngest.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Do you know how old was your father when you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well what he be - he died when he was about fifty so he would be - quite young wouldn't he, between -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 What year did he die?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 I don't know quite what year he died. He died in - I suppose I could go and find out. I'll look it up. Much notice of dates and.-
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 So he was twenty-five years old when you were born, where did he come from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 He came from - }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1463222\charrsid12473461 Lincolnshire}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 . A small - Kirby - just - Kirby - Stanford, just off of Stanford. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1463222\charrsid12473461 
Kirby, C.K. Kirby, how do you spell it, careful how you spell this word 'cos there's a Corby and a Kirby. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
How do you spell Kirby - C.A.B. wasn't it? Oh - 'cos you can get with a - get muddled with Carbey wasn't it, there was a Carbey.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 What did your father do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Well building material he dealt in after he - at first he was - on the railway, was a ganger on the railway and then he had his own business as a building material - secondhand building material at the place at }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid1463222\charrsid12473461 Gospel}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461  Oak. He must have perhaps take that soon after he came to London.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 So when you were born that's what he was doing in }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1463222\charrsid12473461 Gospel}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461  Oak?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. As far as I know, I couldn't know whether he was working at that then or whether he - you know, he was st
ill on the railway but I think he was - it was after he'd met my mother that he must have - started business on his own.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did he do that until he died?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And did that until he died, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 So all the time you were growing up and everything that's what he was doing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, just growing up there in that same house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 So he was self-employed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Self-employed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did he ever do any other part time work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, no, no, he just did that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did he retire or did he work until he died?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 He had illness. He became ill and he had to give up work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Since he was self-employed was he ever out of work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, no, he kept - no, he was - he - had his own - yes, buying }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid81240\charrsid12473461 second hand}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461  material and that was going on all the time which of course was very hard work.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 How old was your mother when you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well - she was about forty-eight when she died, I think it was forty-eight, so she couldn't have been -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 How much younger than your father was she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Not much - two years perhaps.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 He was twenty-five when you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 So she was about twenty-three?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Twenty-three.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Where did she come from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well she lived - she lived there but I don't know whether she was born round there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Lincolnshire?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
No, in London. In Bismall Circus but she lived there but - her father was in the same trade as my father because my father took it from her father. Took it over.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Her father died did he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, no, he - he gave it up. Yes, just gave it up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And your father took it over?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 The he took it over what I can know of it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 So you think your mother was actually born round }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1463222\charrsid12473461 Gospel}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461  Oak?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well, she couldn't have been, I don't know, never know what - some said that she was born in Ame
rica and - and came over here when she was two years old. I think they had, you know, been around a bit.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 But her people came from London?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. That's - I don't really know much about the background of that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did she work at all before she was married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, Id don't think so. No, no, never.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did she work after she married your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. No. No, nothing at all, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did she help him at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 She didn't do the books or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, no. No, she didn't do anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 So there was never any question of someone else having to look after the children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Oh no, no, nobody - she - yes, yes, it was her job.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 How many rooms were there in the house at }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1463222\charrsid12473461 Gospel}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461  Oak?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Let me see, we had the who
le house to ourself and there'd be about two rooms on each floor, one, two, three, four, five, oh I should say be about six rooms altogether.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 How many of them were bedrooms?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well we only had two - I think we only had them as two - two bedrooms l
ike to start off with. While we were - 'cos we was all small, we didn't sort of have a - you know, I don't think in those days it was perhaps one bed each. Don't think it was that then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Two in a bed you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 So the children were two in a bed anyway?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And then a dining room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Yes, we had a - a kitchen, sort of a living room downstairs and then upstairs we had a dining room - no, a lounge - drawing room, a drawing room. But - we also had a - a kind of a frontage 
that was like a shop. My father used to keep a lot of - small articles there such as - everything to do with building you know and - taps and - anything that - valuable that couldn't be kept in the open place.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 So he didn't run the business from there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. Oh no, he - he had this }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1463222\charrsid12473461 Gospel}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461  Oak Brick Fields it was called, a well known place. Yes. That's right, yes, just against the railway and that was a big space, terrific great big space. Two - two ponds there, yes. Matter of fact it was - they used
 to call it, matter of fact years ago it was - used to make bricks there because there's a tall chimney piece and it was brought down, well it was a kind of a shop, you couldn't have a room because it - it got windows all round you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 So originally the front part of the house was a shop?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Must have been a shop, yes, it was made as a shop I should say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did anyone else besides your parents and brother and sisters live in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Ever any other relatives?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Ever any lodgers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Well we did have some once, man - people that my father - he had two working for him. He did sort of let one man have a - a room up the top of the house and his wife and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Would that be for a short while?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well - not - it was for a while, yes, perhaps a year - two years they lived there and - he worked for my father as a labourer.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did your mother pay anyone to help in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. No, she never had any help. Nobody didn't in those days did they, they didn't have anybody in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 It was quite a big house wasn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did she have anybody to help her with the washing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, no, that was all done. We had a kind of a wash house you know like a copper they have in the olden days, you heated the 
copper up and boiled the clothes up in it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 So all the washing was done at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 All the washing was done at home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did your mother or father make or mend any of the children's clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Oh well, yes, all things were mended and - you know, I mean -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Who mended them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Oh mother of course. My father wouldn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Would you do any of the mending?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Yes. We all helped to do the sewing or helped to do shopping.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Would your father ever help mend clothes or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, I don't think in those days -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Or shoes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
No, wasn't necessary. My father was - in a position to pay for that you see. He wasn't in debt you know, unless you was very poor you - they wouldn't do that but I suppose if you were poor w
ell you'd have to do a lot of - which a case they had - well there was - there was poverty I mean it meant the pawn shop mostly that they used to go to.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Where would shoes go to be mended?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Just an ordinary cobblers. Yes. An ordinary cobblers they would be sent to.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Your mother would mend the children's clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Oh yes. Clothes would be mend, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Would she make the clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, she would make clothes, yes.;
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 What about her own clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well - I think - most of them 
were bought. I don't think many were made in those days, not - you know, you didn't have all those clothes. Not like today. Today people buy clothes, they change them every other week. Well in those days we just had - holiday time we had new rig-out and n
e
w boots and they would last and they were kept for Sundays. Yes, you know, for best wear. And - otherwise we - we just I suppose had our ordinary school clothes. We didn't have school uniforms of course in those days. Well, yes, we all - we always kept be
st clothes, we always had best clothes that were kept back. And we always had new ones holiday time, we never had anything in between like they do today.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Would your mother ever buy secondhand clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. No, I don't think we ever had anything - 
no. No, she had made things made for us. She always had things made by a dressmaker. She didn't very often buy things ready made, I don't think they did in them -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 So for the children she'd sometimes have them made by a dressmaker but sometimes she'd make them herself?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, she would, yes. And I make clothes for }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1463222\charrsid12473461 myself}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12473461  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1463222\charrsid12473461 before}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461  I left school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 If she bought clothes for the family or children where would they be bought?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well just local, it would be local. Small shops, yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Wouldn't go into Regent Street?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
No. No, I don't ever remember that we went there, no, the material of course may have came from bigger shops but they were never bought from big shop, it was all local shops, small shops.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 What about something like a new suit for your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, he had his always made. By a - by a tailor that - like had a shop.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Locally?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. In Kentish Town, he always went to that shop always the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1463222\charrsid12473461 same}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461  shop and had it made.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And if your mother had a new coat or dress?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 She had it made by a dressmaker mostly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 When might your father have a new suit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Well - I suppose he'd have a suit you see but it wouldn't be very often. It would be kept for best and - so I suppose it would last perhaps a year or two you see. But of course, our clothes, we did have more naturally, you grow out of them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 So really your father would have a new suit when the other one was becoming worn?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 The - yes, that's right. He would go and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Would he have one for special occasions?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, for special occasion he would always get dressed for a special occasion.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Would he get a new suit for it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Not particular, no, not particular because it was always kept for that occasion, and it sort of was never - taken to work, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did he wear very rough clothes }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid81240\charrsid12473461 when}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461  he went to work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Not really, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did he wear a suit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. A shirt, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And a tie?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, because he had to go to auction sales and he always - always looked nice although he di
dn't have to dress expensive - he always looked clean and tidy.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 He wouldn't wear just rough working clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Oh no, no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Can you remember where the shoes would be bought?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1463222\charrsid12473461 Well - I don't know, I think it would be from a shop perhaps
 been in - been in the - for a long, long while, you know, well established shop such as perhaps -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Locally?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, I couldn't say where, it may have been Kentish Town. And it may have been - what's the - I can't think of the name. Yes, Kentish To
wn or Camden Town. Or of course there was Queens Crescent, that was another shopping centre but as far as I can remember it was you know just local, Kentish Town or }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1463222\charrsid12473461 Camden}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461  Town but I don't think we ever went to the West End, never.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did your father ever help your mother with any of the jobs in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, I don't think so, no, he would make morning tea and he'd cook the morning breakfast you - yes, he would do that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 For all of you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, he would do that. And he was always early riser, six o'clock and have tea.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Would he make early morning tea first?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, then he'd go out and open his place and he'd come back and have his breakfast about eight o'clock I remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And he'd make the breakfast?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Sometimes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 For the whole family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. And then he would - and I suppose we went to school and things went on.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Anything else he would do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well he was very clean, tidy man you see and - I think he would - he had any jobs that had got to be done like heav
y jobs were done by him. Such as ordering coal and things like that in the house and he always paid those bills.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did he ever help with the cleaning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, no, he never cleaned, no, in the house at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Cooking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. Yes, he would just - just did the breakfast but he would never - of course he wasn't there during the daytime.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Washing up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, he would wash up I think, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Very often?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Occasionally if it was necessary but of course we were all there so I suppose we must have done it between us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Making the fires?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Yes, he would make the fire, yes, he would light the fire first thing in the morning. Well yes, he would light the fire first thing in the morning in the living room.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Decorating?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, he never did any decorating, no, he didn't do that type of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Who would do that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Well - we didn't have a lot of decorating done. The premises belonged to the railway and they never did it so nobody did much to that place. It was -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You didn't have any wallpapering or painting done?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Yes, I can't remember who did that. I think if it was done it would be done by an outsider you know. Yes, somebody would come in and do it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And repairs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, that would be the same. No, he never had anything to do with them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 What about improvements to the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, no. I wasn't belong which you couldn't do that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 How did that come that it belonged to the railway?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well all that belonged to the railway. And all the - round to
 the - his business belonged to the railway. All that ground. The land belonged to the railway.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did he ever dress or undress the children for bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, no, no, I - well I think we did that mostly ourselves, and we were brought up to do that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Would he ever bath or wash any of the children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, no, I don't think so, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Would he ever read to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, no. No, never read, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Or tell you stories?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Even on Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, I don't think so, we went to Sunday school Sunday afternoon and - and mostly consisted of walks then, walks in the evening.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 He wasn't one for telling stories?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did he ever take any of the children out without your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Oh yes, yes, he'd go for a walk over Parliament Hill fields - in the evening.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Just himself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Yes. The evening of course was always taken up because he always did his garden in the evenings and grew his own vegetables up there everything. Grew - grew 'em all and then he used to work wh
en he'd finished doing his work and he'd go round the garden, his allotment.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And sometimes he'd take you for a walk without your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Oh yes. Yes, he liked walking being a countryman. He - he -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 He must have liked Parliament Hill Fields?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, he went right across there. Used to have a dog and take it for a walk.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Would he ever look after the children in the house when your mother had to go out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 I don't know how that would be because - I suppose - in those days mother never 
went out anywhere you see. She never went out unless she went out with him.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 She didn't go to any sort of church meetings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. No, no, no. Suppose it took her all her time to look after six children. And - but they did - I think we did - you kno
w, did have day out now and again, that's all that we - never went away. All together. A day out together.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Where?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Oh we'd go by - pony and trap out for a day's outing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 What sort of place would you go to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Oh just like Bushey Heath or somewhere locally, not far but to us it was a long way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did you hire the trap?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, it belonged to my father.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 He kept his own trap?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 He kept his own - and a pony or horse.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 So there was a stable at the house at }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1463222\charrsid12473461 Gospel}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461  Oak?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Oh no, no, that was kept at his business you see because it was a big place. A very big place.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 The trap was kept there as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 But sometimes you'd all go in the trap?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 All go.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You'd take food would you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, I think we would, we wouldn't eat out, no, you never ate out in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You'd go for the whole day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did you have any particular job you were supposed to do in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, I used to do some cleaning. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 It would be the same cleaning every day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well - when I was home I suppose. I suppose you - you help washing up, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Was there a particular job you had to do when you came home from school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, I don't think so, you sort of all - all helped, all sort of - did somet
hing. During that age of course, I mean, at - about nineteen eleven of course would only be about - wouldn't be very old - nine.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You often did the washing up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. And - and cleaning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 How long did you go on doing that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well I - I never went out to business at all. You carried on.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 So until 1930 when you moved?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Until your parents died you continued to help in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Help keep house, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did any of your sisters or brother have any particular tasks?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. My eldest sister, she learnt typing, shorthand typing helped my father with that side of the work, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 When she did that did she work regular hours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Well she went in each day to get it done. And of course she was paid for it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Would she come home at the same time and go to work every morning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, she'd do it in the house. She had a typewriter there and everything. So she did it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 She would put in a good number of hours every day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Oh yes, yes. When - then when she was doing that she - I was perhaps dong the cooking or cleaning or - or we did it between us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Your father would give her the work that had to be done?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Yes, and she would do it, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And you'd be doing the cooking and cleaning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And then Peggy was younger?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 What would she be doing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Oh well just playing I suppose. Just - nothing in particular.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And what would your brother be doing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well he was at - well he was at school wasn't he until he was - I suppose he left when he was fourteen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 The two little sisters that died, what did they die of?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 They both died of T.B.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 They were next to one another?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Were they very ill at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. My - the eldest one, she had been married, she was married and had two children by that time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 So it was quite a lot later on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, but my other sister, she died when she was twenty. Had galloping consumption.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And she'd never been married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. No, she was - n
o, she'd been home all that time but her - she'd had a road accident and she never had anything seen to about it, was caught up in a taxi in Regent Street}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1463222\charrsid12473461 . She was a milliner. And so}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461  she was crossing the road a taxi caught her and dragged her along and of course she wouldn't }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid81240\charrsid12473461 be taken to }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
hospital to be examined or anything so of course nothing was done about it and of course in those days it, you know, things weren't stressed such a lot were they. I suppose complications set in and before it was realized tha
t set in and - and she - she wasn't ill for long.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 That was sad.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Quite a tragedy for the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And the other girl was married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 She was married and had two children. Yes. Pat was - the little boy then was about four years old and the little girl was about a year.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 What year did that sister die?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Now what is it - I suppose Pat would be a year old - two years old so Pat's - thirty - nine, I should say she must have - it's very difficult - we came - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 But anyway that was very sad wasn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Yes, yes, it was. It was very - when she - she got it we thought you know, whether she got it - I don't know what it - she developed it and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 People didn't take so much care then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, no, that's right and of course things weren't stressed much with you and the doctors -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And there were no inoculations were there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, there wasn't anything you see and - 'course you was in contact weren't you with so many and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did the older children help the younger children with things they found difficult?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Oh yes, I suppose, yes, must have helped one another, yes, I think so, we had to look }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6245793\charrsid12473461 after one}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461  another. More or less.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 With something like the little ones dressing themselves in the morning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Yes. Yes, we all helped one another. And cooking, yes, the dinner was served up. Served up on the Sunday when we all sat down to dinner always on Sunday together.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Who would serve it up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 My father would always cut the joint.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And your mother would carry in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 The vegetables and that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Would the older girls help her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Yes. We'd all help to wash up. But - we mostly went to Sunday school in the afternoon. Then in the week of course we had a midday lunch coming home from school, you didn't have anything at school those days did you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did the younger children ever help the older children in any way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well - I can't remember how that went about. I suppose we always - all in together sort of thing, you know what I mean.
 We was all there and I suppose whatever wanted doing was sort - we'd just normally do it without any - any fuss.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Or your mother or father would tell you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Yes, my father would be very, you know, strict about behaviour and you know being in too at night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Were you expected to go to bed at a certain time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, we always had to come in about seven o'clock at night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 This is when you were at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, when we was at school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 What time did you have to go to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Oh was in bed by I suppose eight o'clock at night, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And after you left school and were helping in the house at home did you have to go to bed by a certain time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, well we - my father liked us in by ten when he came home, always in at ten o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 This is after you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 So if you went out you had to be in by ten?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, he didn't - yes, we were never out late.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 If you got home by then what time did you usually go to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well soon after, yes, soon after.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 What if you spent the evening at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well we just sit I suppose, I don't know what we just sit there I don't know what we did really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You'd go to bed by what time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well I suppose, perhaps in the summer was up a bit later.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 About half ten?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Yes. Well - no, it was never - would never be ten o'clock. Nine o'clock would be the latest we'd ever go to bed. Yes. When we were at school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 But when you were older?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, we weren't up then much after ten - half past ten 
at night we had to - was all sort of normally went to bed, my father went to bed at same time every night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 What time was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Half past ten.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And you wouldn't stay up after that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. We'd go to bed, all of us, then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Can you remember at what age did you start putting yourself to bed, when you were small did your mother put you to bed?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well I think she saw we was washed and that. But I think we put ourselves to bed, we all went up sort of thing, all went up together.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 At what age do you think you started going to bed on your own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Well I can't remember - when we went - when we went to bed, whether we were just normal went up to bed without any fuss which I think we did. We was told to go to bed and bed we went. And we never read in bed I don't think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 So would you say when you were about seven or eight years old you would just go up the stairs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, just go up, yes, yes. Just go.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did you share a bedroom or a bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And you shared a bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 With one of your sisters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Just two of you in a bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Two. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And there was another bed in the same room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Oh yes, we had two beds in one room 'cos there was very big rooms.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 There were four sisters at one time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 So did they sleep two in one bed and two in the other?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Where did the brother sleep?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 I don't know quite what he - I think he must have slept - can't remember whether he slept downstairs in a room like in another bed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And then there was they youngest one, Peggy, where did she sleep?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well she would sleep with one of us I suppose, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Where would the baby sleep?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well they'd sleep in me mother's room, mostly that was so I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Your mother and father had a bedroom to themselves?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Yes, but I think - where there were babies the babies slept in there, they didn't have separate rooms really the babies then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Can you remember at what age the baby would go into the other room with the sisters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well - you see we weren't really a lot of different in the age between us all. See.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 So the baby might have to go on sleeping in your mother's room for quite some time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Some time, yes, until well - six I suppose we were six years old.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did the house have a bathroom?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. My father converted it into bathroom. Well he put a bath in and run the water up - tap up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 He did this to the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, he did that to the house, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Even though it belonged to the railway?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did he actually do that work himself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Well yes, I suppose he would, yes, he would do that with the help of one of his labourers. He'd have to put - he'd have to put the pipe up you see and - and he used to have to hot the water downstairs and carry it upstairs. And put it in the bath.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 So where did the pipe come in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 That was the cold water tap. We couldn't get hot water.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 So he arranged a cold water tap from downstairs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 To carry the water up to the bathroom?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, that's it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And you carried the hot water up and put it in the bath?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Yes, about five steps it was, a little room on the first landing and we used to heat the water in the copper. And of course the landlord, they never did a thing, never - all my knowledge.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 But that was one fairly big thing your father did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, he did that, yes, it was essential.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 How often would you have a bath?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Oh about once a week. Yes, yes. It was a regular -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Would you all have it together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 All on one day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, that's right. Mostly be on a Friday night. One night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 One after another?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, we'd all have a bath.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 What about your mother and father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 I don't know what - when they had a bath I'm sure. I suppose they must have had another night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 When you were in bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, could have been, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 So you wouldn't really know about that?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, when they had it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 When would you be given clean clothes to put on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Once a week. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Which day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well it must be weekends it sort of would be you see, all had clean clothes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 For Saturday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Well I suppose it would be Saturday so they'd all be cleaned up for Monday washday was always on Monday so mostly 
I suppose we changed all on Saturday. Then - washing was done on Monday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 In which room did the family have their meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 I suppose you would say it's a kind of a kitchen. No, a living room, it would be a living room, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Was there also a scullery?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, there was a scullery, yes, the cooking was done, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 So the family would have their meals in this sort of living room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Living room.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Were there any occasions when they ate in another room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. No, we did on Sunday eat in our room upstairs occasionally on Sunday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Was that the drawing room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 That was the drawing room - front room we used to call it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Were there any special occasions apart from Sundays when you'd eat in there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No I don't think so, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Birthdays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. Because - it'd be up the stairs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Christmas Day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well yes - I don't know, I can't remember, yes, I suppose it - we should Christmas Day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 That'd be like a Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Sunday, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Where did your mother cook?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 In the scullery. Cooking was done in the scullery.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 What did she cook on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 A gas stove. Yes. Just an ordinary gas stove.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 What time did the family have breakfast?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Around about eight o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 This is a full proper breakfast?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did they all sit down together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well most probably we would - the children would. Before they went to school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Just the children together.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 If my father was there he would sit down as well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Would your mother sit down at the same table with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 What did you usually eat and drink?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 I don't know what we had to drink.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did you have anything to drink on the table normally at meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, not with the - not with the dinner. No, we never - only teatime we'd have drink.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Tea?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Tea, yes, usually with tea.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You had dinner middle day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, we had dinner middle day, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Would you have water on the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, we had water, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 But nothing else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Nothing else, no.;
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 What about your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, he never had anything at the table, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 The evening meal was tea?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Just the tea, yes, we had tea.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And you'd drink tea with it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 With the food, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 So your big meal was in the middle of }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6245793\charrsid12473461 the day}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Midday, yes, we had a hot meal then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 What sort of food would you have in the middle of the day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well we'd have hot - hot meat and two vegetables always and a sweet. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Would you ever have soup?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, I don't think we had soup. We didn't have a lot of soup. No, we didn't have soup in our family.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did your mother never used the bones from the meat for soup?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, we used to have that, yes, they were made into a kind of a - well, we used to have a joint about twice
 a week and then if there was a - a bone over it used to be stewed with fresh meat pudding as well to make up the goodness.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 When would you eat that soup?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 That would be midday, we had midday meal with all the vegetables.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Would it be a soup that you'd eat on it's own or a stew?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, more like a stew.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 So that would become the main course?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Main course, yes, that's right, yes, we wouldn't -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 It would be a thick sort of stew?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, it be substance there of vegetables and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Can you remember what sort of things you might have for a sweet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Oh it would be all - all milk puddings and - and suet puddings and boiled puddings like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 They did eat a lot of those things in those days didn't they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. We did
n't have a lot of - we didn't have tinned fruit, no, we didn't have much tinned fruit. We did occasionally have - like tinned stuff.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 What sort of food did you have for your tea?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 I don't think we had much more than bread and jam. Yes. A cup of te
a, I think we only had tea. May have had cocoa. And we had cocoa as well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did the children drink tea?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did you have anything more at all to eat in the evening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 I don't think we did. No, I don't think we had. As we got older w
e had a later meal. My father used to eat a meal about half past nine in the evening. A lightly cooked meal sort of thing, perhaps liver and bacon.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 What did he call that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well he called it his supper and when you live in the country you have a supper don't you. They used to have a supper.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Would your mother sit down with him as well to eat the supper?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 At what age would you be allowed to have the supper as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Oh well, when we was that young age we weren't - didn't have
 supper. We just had tea but when we was older - well, after we'd left school. Yes. We started to cook it, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did you have any sort of different, special food on certain days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. No, we used to sometimes keep Good Friday up, and we always had fish on that day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Were either of your parents Catholic?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. But we always had -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Just a tradition?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6245793\charrsid12473461 Easter time}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461  we always sort of tradition, we had that always Good Friday. Yes. We always sort of had fish on that day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 What about ordinary Fridays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, not particular, no, we - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 We always had a main - joint - hot joint and - everything that goes with it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did your mother or father bake their own bread?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. No, didn't do any of that. Bought all - shop bread.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did she ever make her own jam?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, I think so, yes, and puddings, you know, Christmas puddings were all made.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 If she was making jam where did she get the fruit from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well we - he had allotment with a certain amount
 of bushes. Loganberries, there were blackberries of course around, we used go country and get blackberries and make jam of those.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You'd make an expedition to the country?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And on his allotment he had some fruit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. He had some fruit there, used to cook it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And so she'd make some jam?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did she ever bottle fruit or vegetables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 I don't think we did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Was there anything in the allotment that she would bottle?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Only what - sort of onions, they would be bottled. Shallots. Yes, they would be all done.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did she or your father ever make any wine?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, we didn't have a lot of wine in the house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 They didn't make any?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Or any sort of herbal drink?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. No. He did in his home of course in the country where they do make a lot of wine.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 But he didn't carry it on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. No, not in London.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 He didn't make any beer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 So your father grew his own vegetables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And some fruit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did your mother buy any vegetables and fruit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, she bought some as well during the season when it wasn't in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did she ever buy any tinned vegetables or fruit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. No, I don't think we ever had any tinned vegetables, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Or dried fruit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
No I don't think so. It was mostly - we had such a - a lot of the stuff grown. Of course when it wasn't in season you could buy such good stuff in those days that it wasn't necessary.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did they keep any livestock at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No hens or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Your father had some animals where he did his business?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Dogs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 What were they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Dogs. Just dogs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Didn't you say a pony?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, he did have a sort of a - I suppose - it'd be a pony or it'd be a horse was it. Maybe a horse.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did he look after the horse himself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Well he had men working for him - I suppose they looked after it between them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Could you possibly remember how many times a week you ate meat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Oh we had meat every day. Every day, yes. Yes, for dinner, yes, always had meat.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did you ever have tinned meat at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did you ever get any extra meat like something bought from the country, like a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6245793\charrsid12473461 pheasant}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461  or chicken?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, yes, we used to have turkeys up from the country.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 This is your father's relatives?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Well from the farms near. Rabbits - we used to have a lot of rabbits. Rabbits, yes, we used to have a lot of rabbits.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 How would they send them?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Oh ju
st tied together and send 'em by post - rail, put on at the railway early hours of the morning and they were there in the evening. We used to often have two come along and - very nice.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 They were sent to the railway station?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, they put 'em at the railway station.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 How did you get them from the railway station?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Just hanging together.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Would somebody have to go and collect them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, I think somebody did collect them, yes, they would collect them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You'd be told to go and collect them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Knew they were coming.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You'd know they were coming how, by letter?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, most probably, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Do you ever remember seeing your mother sort of take smaller portions for herself so that there'd be more to go round the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, I don't think I remember that - seeing that, it may have happened.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You never noticed it at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Never noticed it, no. I think one is inclined to do that when you're serving up aren't you 'cos I do it myself. Yes, I do that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 But there was always plenty of food in your family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, we were very fortunate, we always had plenty.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Would she serve your father a bigger portion?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No I don't think so. No. No, I think we was all equally - all equally had the same.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Were you allowed to talk during meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, my father didn't like that. No, he didn't like - no, he didn't like you to talk a lot at meal table.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Would you say it was a strict rule?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well I don't know, I think it was more or less you would sort of
 more or less, would play more when you started to talk you would - what would you say it would be - would say - would call it playing at the table wouldn't you, you know, sort of -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did this just apply to the children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Would your mother and father speak to each other?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Oh yes, I think so. Yes. Yes, my father would carry on a normal conversation with - you know, about everything. Quite happy with what had taken place when he wasn't -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 But he wouldn't like one child to talk to another?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. No. No he didn't like us to carry on a conversation at the table.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Could you choose what you wanted to eat from what was cooked or did your parents insist that you had a bit of everything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well it was all put on our plates and we just accepted it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Your father would cut the meat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Your mother ladled out the vegetables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And handed you the plate?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. We just ate it. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 What happened if there was something you really hated.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well I think, our meals were all more or less plain meals that - I suppose that - didn't cause for any refusal.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You can't remember the children making a fuss about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. No, about anything, no I can't remember. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Would your parents say anything if you did leave some food on your plate?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Most probably, yes, say you must eat it all up, yes. As my father couldn't bear waste. No, he - he was brought up not to waste.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 If there was something on the table you wanted like the salt could you
 ask someone to pass it to you or did you have to wait until it was offered to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 I don't know, I suppose really it was all within our reach, I can't remember any - problem about that at all. No, I can't remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Do you think you would have said to your father, could you pass the salt?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, most probably would have done, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Could you ask for a second helping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. We could always ask for anymore if you wished. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Were you expected to hold your knife and fork in a certain way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, my father liked that. Yes. And to sit at the table properly. Yes. Sit properly at the table.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You couldn't slouch?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Oh no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Could you bring toys or a book to the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, no, that was never allowed, no, nobody a
llowed reading at the table, no, we never read at the table. My father - no, my father never read at the table.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And you wouldn't bring a toy to the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, no he wouldn't - he wouldn't have had anything like that at the table.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 When could you leave the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well I think we all left more or less when we thought it was the right time to leave.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 All together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 So if you finished first would you wait for the others?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. Well, yes, I think we would, yes. Yes. We all sort of got up together.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 All the family sat at the table together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Together, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did you always sit in the same places?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes I think so, yes, I think she did, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did your mother put all the food together on one plate for each person and then hand you the plate?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 So she handed you your plate with your meat and veg and everything on it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You didn't help yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Who would she serve first?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 I don't think anybody in particular, I can't remember it was anybody in particular, that was served first.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did she begin with the eldest?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, no I don't think so, I think was - as the meat was put on the plates the plates were put round you know, sort of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Where did the younger ones sit and eat while they were babies?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 I can't remember right that way back. No, I can't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Do you think they had anything like a high chair?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, most probably they would have a high chair.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Would they sit at the table with the rest of the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, I don't ever remember a high chair being there but -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Were there any special rules for babies?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 It was all the family together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You can't remember then who fed the baby?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, no, I can't remember that much back. All being round about the same age you see you're close that -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Would you say your mother was an easy person to talk to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You weren't afraid of her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Would you say that she showed affection to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 She was quite loving?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 If you were worried about anything could you tell her about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 What about your father, was he an easy person to talk to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Would he show affection to the children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Oh yes, he would - accept anything you ask him or - or give you anything you ask within reason.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Would he hug or kiss the children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, I don't think any of that went on, no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 When you were little, babies?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. No, I can't remember right back. Right back that date really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did you kiss your mother or father goodnight?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. No. No, I don't remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 If you had any worries could you go and tell your father about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, I think we would have done, yes, if we'd been any.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 If you were worried about anything would you go to your mother or your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well - most probably my mother mote than me father because he would be sort of busy he wasn't in all the time and he -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 How do you think your parents expected you to behave towards them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well - we had to keep our place sort of thing, you know, weren't allowed to - be cheeky or -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You had to show respect?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Respect, yes, yes, well of course he was also very quiet really that -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You were all quiet as children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, more or less, yes, we sort of all -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You weren't very rowdy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, no I don't think so, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Of course it was five girls wasn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. We did have a few squabbles with brother, you know, have a -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Since he was the youngest and the only boy was he made a special pet of?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, he was - no, he wasn't made a pet but he was sort of - you know, thought a lot of sort of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Would you say that when he was young, still at school, did he have to help in the house just like the girls?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No I don't think so, no. No, he was always getting into trouble outside, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Was he ever expected to do anything like wash up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, I don't think he was, no, I think - think it was more or less the girls in those days that had to do things, I don't think boys -

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Can you remember any particular job the little boy had to do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, don't remember him doing anything, only fall over and hurt himself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Until he left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 'Til he left school, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 did your parents bring you up to behave in a certain way towards your brother and sisters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 What did they mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well - don't know quite what you would say there -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did they feel that you should love your brother and sisters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well we sort of all got on well together I sort of - you know, you sort of -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Was your father annoyed to see you squabbling?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. He couldn't bear that. No, he didn't like you to quarrel at all. N
o, he was a quite man and he didn't like to see anybody quarrel so of course we didn't - never quarrel in front of him, if we did when he'd gone out, we may have had little difference then. Over some - over some trifle that - toy or - something. But when 
he was there it was perfect quietness.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You wouldn't dare to start?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 If another child hit you do you think your father would say that you ought to hit the child back?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, no, don't think so. He'd get very }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6245793\charrsid12473461 whatsisname}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461  about it, my mother would get very cross about it if anybody hit us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Cross that another child hit you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 But they wouldn't say?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, I don't they think they would - no, take much notice of it outside.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Do you think your father preferred his children to be peaceful?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Yes. He didn't like any disturbance, no. No, he didn't like any violence at all.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 What kind of people do you think your parents hoped you'd grow up to be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well I don't quite know what -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did your father have any particular hopes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, I don't think so, no, he sort of - he seemed to be quite happy the way things were going always.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did he have any hopes about the girls or any particular ideas about whom he'd like them to marry?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, no, he sort of always sort of was pleased whatever we did. Because it was very little we did besides, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 What about his son, did he have any particular hopes for him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well I suppose he did have hopes of him going into the business and helping which he did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did they ever say anything about the kind of people they'd like the children to grow up to be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, I don't ever remember that coming up in the conversation at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did they bring you up to consider certain things important in life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Well I suppose - the - everyday life like we led going to Sunday school and going to bed at the right time and not going out in the street and getting rough, you know, living an ordinary life, you can't - go against that much can you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 So it was important to your mother and father for you to be respectable?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Yes, that's it, and not to go out anywhere. Which of course there wasn't a lot of - temptation was there then I mean.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 I suppose there'd be some children playing in the street?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Well, yes, there would but - I suppose after it started getting dusk and that you came in. Of course when you came in you went to bed because there's nothing else to do, I mean you had nothing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 What did they think of swearing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, we didn't swear.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did the boy ever swear?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, I don't ever remember. And father never used language, no, no, he never used any language.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Were you allowed to join in when grown-ups were talking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. No, they never - spoke in front of us. Other people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 They wouldn't discuss anything grown-up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, no, no. No, nothing was discussed like - that wasn't fit for a child to hear like -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 If somebody came to see your parents and they were talking would you be allowed to join in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, no, we - never say anything. Don't know why but -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
At meal time with just the family together, if your mother and father were speaking together about something that had happened during the day.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 We never joined in, no. No, we kept quiet.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Would your father maybe say something to one of you about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well - yes, he could do, he could join us in a conversation in a way that -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 He might ask you a question?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Question, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 It was a real case of you didn't speak until you were spoken to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Spoken to, yes, that's right, we just sat there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 If you did something that your parents disapproved of what would happen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well - I suppose we would get more or less reprimanded about it but nothing - nothing serious, we never - never 
punished in any way. No. No, never punished. I can't remember being punished. Be perhaps kept in, we weren't allowed to go out
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Who would say you should be kept in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Mostly my mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 She would actually keep you in herself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You mean keep you in, not let you out to play?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Not let us out, no, }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6245793\charrsid12473461 brought}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461  indoors and door bolted.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You say you were never actually physically punished?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, never, never.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 The only thing you can think of is being kept in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 In, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Do you remember any particular occasion when you were kept in for something?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, it would only be perhaps at night when we - you know, wanted to come in, sort of made to come in early then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Can you remember what it was you'd done?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Not - not really, nothing - nothing very much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 What sort of thing would it be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Well maybe it'd be perhaps doing something we should have done perhaps and had gone out without doing it. Little job perhaps. Or perhaps with regard to ourselves, something we hadn't done for ourselves, washed properly or something like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 She'd say you come in early?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Can you remember how you felt when that sort of thing happened? Did you feel very resentful?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well - yes, you felt, you know, as if you had been punished sort of thing although it was so slight.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did you feel that you had been a bad child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Child, yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Would you say that when you were growing up like that you got your ideas on how people behaved from your mother or from your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Well I suppose - well I suppose both my mother and father, you see, there were both sort of - sort of quiet. They behaved in front of us. And always seemed to be, you know, going - doing the right thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 When it came to telling you how people should behave towards each other would it be your father or your mother who influenced you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well I suppose it'd be my mother really, my father didn't interfere more really. He didn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 So you think your mother really gave you your ideas?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, yes. Well my father left it to my mother I suppose. He wasn't with us much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 He would disapprove if you didn't behave?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, he - he would if he didn't like anything he would say he wouldn't - didn't like it, he wouldn't have it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You said he didn't like it if you squabbled with each other?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Squabble - squabble or did - played games on Sunday or did something like that that he didn't like you see. And my mother used to say, well don't do it, you can't do that in front of your father, you mustn't sew on Sundays.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 When she said that, do you think if your father had been away she would say well it's all right, you can sew?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, I don't think so. No, I don't think she would have done. I don't think -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You think she had the same ideas really?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And you said he didn't like to see you with a needle in your hand on Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, on Sunday, no, if we did use a needle we didn't do it in front of him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You mentioned that he didn't like you to play games?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, no. Well games weren't played much on Sunday were they so that was sort of easy wasn't it Sunday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 But you did have a hot meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Oh yes. We had a hot meal every day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Including Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 When you had a birthday would it be different from any other day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
No. No. We would have something bought us perhaps and it was shared between us. You see, sort of thing. No, no special meal or anything like that I don't think there would be.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Just the one present?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Nothing special to eat and no visitors?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No I don't - no, no we never had any visitors.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Any cards?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, no, no cards much sent in those days, that's strange isn't it. More or less, I never - we never had a card, I don't 
know that it was sent much in those - I'm sure it wasn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did they have Christmas Cards?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Yes, I think we had Christmas cards. But it wasn't like they do today. We didn't get - didn't have cards all round everywhere - you get dozens now. But in those days I suppose you had one from - the parent of that house and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Can you remember anything you did with your mother or father together on Christmas Day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, I think we did. We always used to have a very nice meal Christmas Day all together
 and, you know, all the things that went with and we always used to have our stockings hung up at - we only used to have fruit in them but we didn't have any toys much but we - every Christmas we all had a toy - all had a stocking full of this fruit. It w
as put in after we'd gone to bed and it was always there in the morning, of course that was quite - quite a thing really, we thought quite a lot of that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did you go anywhere special on Christmas Day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did you have any musical instruments in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 We had a piano. We had -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Who played the piano?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well - we all tried to play but none of us was successful with it 'cos we didn't practice.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You told me that you had lessons?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, we had a few lessons but we didn't keep them up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Where did you have the lessons?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 In the house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did somebody come?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And you didn't keep them up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, we didn't keep them up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 None of you showed any special interest?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 After you got tired of the lessons did any of the children keep on playing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, we used to amuse ourself with just the five finger exercise and just get a tune out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Only the piano then - was there any other musical instrument at all in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, only a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6245793\charrsid12473461 gramophone}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 , sort of a - what you call a - horn kind of thing, that's all we had.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And some }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6245793\charrsid12473461 records}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And we had }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6245793\charrsid12473461 records}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461  to go with it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 When you played records on it did you sit around and listen to them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, we sat and listened to them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did you ever dance to them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 I don't think we danced really. No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Was there anyone in the family who sang?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, no, we never really sung any of us, no musical in our family at all. My father used to sing a b
it. He tried to during holiday times, used to get up and do a little song and dance.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did you ever make music together as a family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 We used to sang together, yes, my sister used to play the piano and we used to stand round the piano and sing it s
ort of thing, sing with her.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Popular songs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Popular songs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Hymns?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, mostly popular songs that were out during that time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did your parents play any games at all with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, we never had any games, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Were there any books in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, we didn't have a lot of books. No, we didn't read a lot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 If there were some books what sort of books were they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well - as far as I know, I can't remember, we had any books really, not -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Do you remember a bookcase?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, we didn't have a bookcase, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Any newspapers around the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 I can't remember whether my father had a newspaper or not, I don't think he did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Can you remember him often reading a newspaper?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 He could have - mornings.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Do you ever remember your mother or father reading?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, don't remember. My father's - time seemed to be taken up when he came home to eat and then to wash and then -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did you ever see your mother reading a magazine?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, never - they never read.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did they ever read aloud to each other or to the children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. No. No. No, no.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Do you ever remember a funeral in the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, I think I do, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Who would attend the funeral? There was your sister who had the accident and got T.B. and died, who came to that funeral?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, a few relatives.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And all the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, and the -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did you wear mourning clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, all mourning, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 How long after did you wear it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Quite - nearly months. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Six months?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, I think we did near enough. You didn't go into bright }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6245793\charrsid12473461 colours}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461  after that, you sort of wore mauve which was quite a - half mourning. But nearly everybody that was anybody went to the funeral in black, nearly all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And the family had to wear the deep mourning for quite some time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Yes, I think it was the time was about six months they stayed in black.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Were you taken out to visit neighbours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No we never visited - visited - made much of visiting neighbours. No, we didn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Were you friendly with the neighbours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Just for a morning - good morning, something like that. Just how do you do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You didn't go in their houses?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Never went in their homes, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Were you taken out to visit family friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, only our own relatives. Yes. No, we didn't go and visit - friends.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Would you go and visit them on your own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. We'd go on our own because they were nearly all local.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Sometimes would your mother or father take some of the family or all the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Well I suppose - my father wasn't a man that went visiting. He didn't make a habit of ever going visiting and - I suppose we just normally went on our own, just -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 When you were old enough?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. I know it was family that we went away for like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Up to Kirby?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, or anything like that used to go then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Were you taken shopping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, I think we all used to go shopping.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Who would take you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Naturally - mostly my mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 This was when you went to buy some shoes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 That's right, yes, my father would still be working all the time you see, he didn't have any time off being his }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6245793\charrsid12473461 own boss}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461  he always had to be - yes, work all the time excepting - well, after midday Saturday, he 
worked always Saturday mornings I think he did. Just had Sunday then didn't they and Sunday - Saturday evening off.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did you ever go out with just your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Not while my mother was alive - I don't think, I think we all - when we went out for d
ays outing or anything we all went together. It was a day out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 With mother and father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You can't remember any time when you'd go out with just your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, no, I don't think ever did, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Didn't you say sometimes you might go for a walk with him in }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6245793\charrsid12473461 Parliament}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461  Hill fields
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Yes. He always went for a walk over Parliament fields on Sunday I think, it was Sunday 'cos that was the only day he didn't -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Would he take you with him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, we could go if we wished. Di}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6245793\charrsid12473461 d}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 n't }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6245793\charrsid12473461 force}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461  us to go but we went if he - if we wanted to.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Do you remember any other outings with your parents like on Bank Holidays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well - yes, used to have a day at the seaside sometimes perhaps - Southend was the nearest place went to. Ye
s. Well you could go from Kentish Town, }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6245793\charrsid12473461 Gospel}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461  Oak we could go to from there, that day, yes, go right through.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 That would be a regular summer thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well it would be perhaps - we'd do it perhaps only the once in the summer and then it would -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Would you make it on a Bank Holiday or a special day like Easter Monday or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Yes, most probably it would be on a special holiday time that we'd do that or if we went away like up to the country it would always be during }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid81240\charrsid12473461 your}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461  school holidays, we all went together.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did you ever go away for a holiday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, not alone.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 If you went to Kirby to your father's relatives?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, he would have taken then left.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Your father and mother would take you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And leave you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And the same when you had to come home?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Oh no, yes, that's right, we never came by ourselves.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 So you didn't travel by yourselves?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, no, we never travelled by ourselves, not 'til a certain age.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 What age?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well - I don't know about - I think - maybe I'd be about eighteen before I did that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Was it because your mother and father didn't think young children should travel in trains on their own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, I don't think it was that really, I just don't think - t
hey ever did that much really. I suppose they may have done in some families but we never - never went alone, always went with a parent.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 When you did go to Kirby like that in the summer how long did you stay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 We sometimes stay a month there. And
 we'd be there and go in the harvest and go out in the fields. Then catching the rabbits. Then playing cricket in the evening with all the country boys and girls. And of course we did have a lot of rain during our school holidays. We enjoyed it. Hated goi
ng home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You'd go every year?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Yes. We went every year until we got to the certain age, we got so accustomed I had - used to go alone sometimes and stay with a - another relative down there. We'd all go together but I would stop at a certain place in Stamford with another }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6245793\charrsid12473461 auntie}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
 or relative. And she had three sons and she always wanted me to go there. She wanted me to live with them and my mother and father wouldn't let me go. But as we grew older we was left there during our summer holidays.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And they just came and fetched you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 They never stayed more than a weekend when they came and fetched you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, no, I don't think so, no, it was a very small cottage. Very tiny cottage, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 When you were there you said you were there for the harvest and things like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Harvest, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did your grandparents know farmers locally?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well - they lived there for many years I suppose they must have known every farmer around.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 So you'd help local farmers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, I do
n't think we helped, we went in - they let us go with them you see. Yes. And we used to go in the farms and go down there and see them milking the cows and the animals, which was very interesting.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And you said you played cricket?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, we used to play cricket with the village children up on the green.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Were they just }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6245793\charrsid12473461 children}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461  games or proper organized games?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Oh just - well we used to play cricket properly you know, my brother had the cricket stumps and we'd all go out and play. Until it 
got dark.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Was there anything special you did in the evenings?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
No, no, we went walking. Used to go for some walks along the lanes then we - when mostly it was getting dark we used to come in, we never stayed out late.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Could you tell me how you spent Saturdays at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Saturday, I don't think we did anything special, it may have been shopping. May have been shopping was done Saturday. And - maybe one of us may have visited a relative, 'cos we had my mother's people lived a few yards awa
y from us. We used to just - just used to go round and call on them. I suppose we all went our way. We had friends. Young girl friends, yes, young friends that we went out with.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 When you went out with them where would you go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well - it would just be a walk or - my sister sometimes went on the lake, rowing. Regents Park.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Two girls together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 How did you spend Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well I think we mostly had to help in the morning, you know, potatoes and chopping mint and help get the d
inner and then - I think after lunch we would go out or go to Sunday school. Mostly went to Sunday school I think. We came home, we'd have our tea and sometimes there'd be a walk in the evening just over the - we nearly all went over the park.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 With your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 With my father or friends, with friends that we'd got, young friends. Yes, then just home in the evening.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And you'd have something to drink when you came home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, we'd have a meal then, yes, supper. Yes, we'd - it was mostly s
ort of - you mostly had a supper that was - cold meat and - all cold stuff for meal and have some potatoes and things.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 The things that you'd had for lunch really?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You did have special clothes for Sunday didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Oh yes, we always dressed up for Sunday in all our best clothes, clean, yes, shoes and everything }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid81240\charrsid12473461 else}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461  as you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did you play games on Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, no, no games were played on Sunday, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did your parents think it was wrong to work or play on Sunday, you told me your father was very particular about work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Yes. Yes, he didn't -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Not even a needle in your hand?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, he - he didn't think anything should be done that was unnecessary on Sunday. He never did anything. He may have gone
 to his allotment but I think they - I don't know whether he did that even, to get fresh vegetables for lunch.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 All you were really allowed to do was the cooking and washing up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, the cooking and the washing up and we didn't do anything else. 
Went to Sunday school and I think most probably the rest of the day was spent in walking.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Could you sit down and read if you wanted to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Oh yes, we could read, we were allowed - we would do anything we liked you know father I suppose most like -
 he would sleep in the afternoon perhaps for a short while, being the only day he could do that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
When you went for a walk in the evening and came home, would your father go out any more himself? Or would he have anyone come in to see him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, we never had visitors. We didn't have - friends in, no, it wasn't a thing that we had. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Do you think it was usual?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well I think it was a usual run of things myself. I don't think people - did go into neighbours so much as they do today. Perhaps
 if you lived in the country they did, we did there. The door was always open in the country, I mean you was backwards and forwards. But it is different you see, we - we speak to people of course and next door neighbour but - we never went into their home
s, I can't ever remember going into their homes at all. My father never did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did your parents go to church or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, no, they didn't go to church.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Or any sort of mission or anywhere like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, I don't think they did. No. Although
 my father was brought up - in the country and went to church there but - when he came to London I don't think he went.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 If somebody asked him his religion what would he have said?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Church of England, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And your mother too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did you go to church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, we went to Sunday school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did you go to a service on Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Sometimes we went in the evening, early evening, I think it used to be six o'clock I think the evening used to start and we used to go but we didn't m
ake a - and I think we had a kind of a Band of Hope there called it, you know, to do with the church. We went there like - like a club, you could go round that to the church hall.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And you'd go to Sunday school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. We go in their outings then you see. Yes, we had Sunday school outings.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 How often would they be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well you'd only get them once a year, then we'd all go that - the whole day out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 It used to be a whole day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Where, to the country?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, it was mostly 
I think to the seaside, no, Epping. We went there quite a lot there to Epping Forest. There used to be - a fair there and all sorts of things like that and we'd spend the day there.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Would you have a picnic?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And have a picnic, I think we used to have to take our sandwiches and I think they had a set tea for all the children later before we }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6245793\charrsid12473461 left}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461  to come back home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Where would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 In Epping.;
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 In a hotel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Oh no, it would be under a marquee or out in a - in a -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Who would set that up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Well it'd be kind of just - it wasn't elaborate of course. I think - I suppose it would do - should be do either with the church or the school I suppose would pay for that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Would the people who were taking you on the outing bring all that with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, I think you could get }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid81240\charrsid12473461 that}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461  there most probably. I can't think if we got it there or whether we took our sandwiches and drink with us but I don't think that was so because I think we could get the stuff when we got there, you 
bought it we had money, you bought your things you required. 'Cos I went with a girlfriends as well and she'd eaten too much and it made her bad and she go into trouble when she got home for that, being bad, she got punished.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 It made her bad?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You mean sick?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, made her sick and bad so her mother punished her for - her mother punished her for eating too much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 I should think she was punished already with being sick?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well they were very strict people I think. Her mother and father. I can clearly remember that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Were there any other outings organized by the church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, they'd have school treats. They called them school treats, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 What would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 That would be a days out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did you go on those?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, we went on them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 So they would be more days out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Yes. I don't whether we went by brake, you know, horse and brake, yes, and we'd all go by one of those. Can't remember if it was at the sea or not but -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And this was to do with the Sunday school as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
That was to do with the Sunday school, yes, you could go you see if you belonged to the Sunday school. But it would only happen perhaps once a year.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And there wasn't anything else organised just for the church, like bazaars?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 I don't think so, no, I don't think there was much of that done in those days. Such a great deal. I can't -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You don't remember going to any little socials?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Can't remember that. I can't remember if we ever had any of those like they 
do today, they have a lot don't they. Well it's mostly for - they do it for charity don't they today. But -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did you belong to the choir?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did the chapel or church run any sort of temperance club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 That I can't say. I know there was 
a Boys - Brigade, you know, the Boys Brigade. Most probably that was a thing separate from the schooling wouldn't it be because they used to join that and they - very nice they were.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Was grace said at meals in your family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, not in our home. I
t was in some of my father's peoples homes, always before. My auntie's home, she'd say grace and she always read a few lines out of the Bible when breakfast was over. When breakfast was over she'd read just a few lines. Before the day started.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Were you taught to say prayers at night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, not really, not in our home. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You never had family prayers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Do you know if your father took an interest in politics at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 He was - yes, he was keen - very interested in that, yes, 'cos he - he would always have liked to have become - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Do you know what his views were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well I know they were very Conservative. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Do you think he was a man who believed in law and order?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Yes. He never looked down on an
y body else, everybody was - he thought every body was as good - he as good as anybody else sort of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Even though he had his own business?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 He treated his men the same as he would treat a relative or brother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 He believed in free enterprise?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 That people should be able to make their own way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Yes, that's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Why do you think he believed like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well they - because it - his own life most probably, he - he made his own way. He'd had to fight, yes. Sort of - since he was quite young.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did he ever actually belong to a political party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. His time was taken all up with his business.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 What about your mother - did she take any interest at all?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. Not in outside - don't think she took any interest in outside, no outside, no It was mostly the home and - children and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 She didn't have a vote until later did she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 How would she have voted if she had do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 I think she would have done exactly as my father w
ould have wished - would have thought the same as him, I mean, she thought what he did was right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Do you remember your father voting in a general election at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, I can't remember that. Whether they had an election or not. He's always very interested he was, in anything like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And you're pretty sure which party he would have voted for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Because they used to have a lot of meetings in - up Parliament Hill fields and he'd be very keen to stand and listen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And you think he'd have voted for the Conservatives?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, oh yes, I think he was that more way, yes. I don't know if they did have a vote in those days, did they, when -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Women did you say?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, women didn't have votes, not until some -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Your mother wouldn't have had would she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, I don't think so, no, men only had the votes. Suffragette when did she - 1911 wasn't it. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 In some places at that time men felt they might lose their jobs if they didn't vote like their boss and things like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Do you think that your father may have felt that because he was a business man and an employer and he owned his own business that he should vote Conservative?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Most probably he thought it was his right thing to do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 It would be his duty as a man who employed other people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Yes. Yes, he thought it was right that he should be Conservative.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You don't remember him taking part in any political meetings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. No. No, he didn't take part in anything like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 He'd just stand and listen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, he would just stand and listen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 When your father wasn't doing his work how would he spend his time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well - when he came home it was fairly late, I mean, you didn't finish early in those days. He'd come home and he'd have a -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 About what time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Six or seven. The time he came home it was getting late because he'd go on his allotment garden before he came home and then it would be getting dusk. And then he would wash and then he would go out and have a drink. He would always went out for a drink.

\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 This was before his meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, late - last thing of night he would go out, after everything was done, he'd have his wash when he came home from the garden.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Had his meal then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. No, he used to have his - about teatime he used to have his tea. And we used to take it up to him sometimes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 So there was tea then he'd come home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Then he'd come home about half past nine to ten and he'd have his supper then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 So you take the tea up to him at half four or five o'clock?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, that's right. Yes, that's right, he'd have some tea.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And then he'd come home later?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 About six or seven, but on the way he'd go to his allotment?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, his allotment was where he worked.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Then when he got home about six or seven he would wash?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And then later on he would go out and have a drink?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 He would go out and - yes, very often did business in - he would meet somebody there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And then when he came back would he have his supper?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Then he'd have his supper when he come back and he would go to bed, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And you say he would often meet somebody who he'd be doing business with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, they often met in the pub, we didn't have any - visitors home. I don't think they did go into people's homes quite so much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And he probably preferred to keep that outside anyway?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, they - yes, that type of business especially.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did your mother have any interests outside the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No I don't think so because she had her own relatives around and - when you was a fairly big family that could take quite a time up.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 When she wasn't working what would she do with her free time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well I don't know what she would do, I suppose she'd be, 
sort of once the tea - got our tea over she'd sort of be getting us ready for bed almost as we was in by seven at night. And I think she did go out with my father in the evening, lat evening, once we were all in bed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Would she go to the pub with him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Yes, they would just go and have a drink or they would go shopping together Saturday night. Some people I suppose that do have some definite thing in life you know that, like living with a father that was a drunkard or a - a fighting and all that, yo
u would remember that case, it was outstanding wouldn't it.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 But when you have a happy .....?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well just an ordinary smooth and things the same every day you don't -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You went to school didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 How old were you when you first went to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well I suppose I went with the usual - start at five. Five.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 When you first started school what time of the morning did you go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 I think we - we went to school at nine o'clock in the morning. I think we started at nine.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 When did you come back?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 I think - I forget what time we finished.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did you go in the afternoon as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 We came back midday for lunch. Home for lunch.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You came back midday for lunch?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And did you go back in the afternoon at the very beginning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Then go back to school, yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Even as a child of five you went to school morning and afternoon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Yes, I think we must have done, yes, and perhaps we all come home together 'cos we'd all be at school at a
 certain time then wouldn't we - through so many years and - we'd come home to lunch then go back again most probably I suppose school would finish - perhaps four thirty in those days, I think it did go longer didn't it than today.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 What kind of school was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 A very modern school. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Was it a private school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Oh no, no, a - a - ordinary state school. Well what do you call them? Just Mansfield Road school. Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Was it boys and girls mixed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Yes, it was boys and girls mixed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 How did you get there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Walked.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 How long did it take you to walk there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Oh I suppose ten minutes. It's quite a near school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Who went with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Oh I think we went alone, we always went the same direction, you know, short cuts through.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Each one went alone?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 I don't know if we }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid81240\charrsid12473461 all}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461  sort of danced away one after another, I suppose we did. As we were ready for school we just went.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You said you came home for your midday meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 What did you think of school, did you like it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, no, I didn't care for school very much. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6245793\charrsid12473461 
Never seemed to very happy there, nobody seemed to - nobody seemed to bother about you much. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You just went through the lessons and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Would you say you were actually unhappy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Well, I wouldn't say unhappy, you just - just went and - that was all, and you - we there was one or two lessons you were interested in I was in - perhaps sewing and - I don't know what I knew, I suppose I wasn't very bright or otherwise I may ha
ve been interested.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Nobody particularly tried to draw you out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, I suppose they had a lot in the class in those days, you just -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 How many in the class do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Oh quite a lot in the class, I can remember the classroom seemed to
 be very big - thirty or forty children I should think. Big now. And they were very big classrooms there, it's a lovely school, you know, }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6245793\charrsid12473461 nicely}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461  built, nice playground in those days I mean it was very modern.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 How did you feel about the teachers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Well some teachers seemed to be better than others, I think it was a schoolmaster, perhaps we was all afraid of. He was rather a - unbending sort of a man. But we didn't sort of come in contact with him much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 He was the headmaster?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Headmaster, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did the teachers emphasise certain things as being very important, what about manners?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
She would praise you for anything. I can remember her praise - I remember she praised me once and that always sort of - I think when you're praised at sc
hool like that it always stands out, bit of praise. Brought me out the class and said, this is the way you should come to school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did she mean the way you were dressed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Dressed, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 She thought you were neat and tidy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. And I was dressed just nice that morning I - I was - matter of fact it was clothes that I'd all made myself and gone to school in.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 It's amazing to think of a child under fourteen making all these clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. I remember it, a pretty white blouse and a re
d slip and it did look nice, I can remember it so clear, that, yet there's other things I can't remember much. I sort of, you know, could always gazing out the window - wasn't interested. Can't remember anything I was interested in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Were the teachers very keen on tidiness?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, I think they was, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And manners?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. And strict they were, I mean, you were soon sort of punished.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 How would they punish you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Oh, just put you outside the door.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Would they hit you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well they - yes, they would clip you. Yes, I had one man teacher, he was very bad. He clipped me round the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6245793\charrsid12473461 face}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461  once, I can remember that very clearly. I think myself that must perhaps have been the mixed - 'cos there was boys and girls, I think as we got older -

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 If you were clipped round the face like that would you tell your mother about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, I - yes, and she would be very indignant. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Even if you had been naughty?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Oh yes, she would feel like going up you see, whether she went -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Even if you had been naughty?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6245793\charrsid12473461 Yes, she'd still be indignant about it but of course that they could hit you.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Were they very keen on punctuality?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, yes, my father was very keen about that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Were the teachers very particular about being on time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, I think we - I don't ever remember being late while was there. I think we was afraid to be late.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 What about ways of speaking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, I think we always treat - approached a teacher the right way because I think it wa
s way we was sort of brought up. Don't think you was ever cheeky to teachers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 If you did something the teachers didn't approve of they might punish you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Yes, I think you had lines, I think we did have lines to write and kept in in the playt
ime to do that instead of being allowed out to play.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Otherwise the teachers would hit you if they felt like it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well I think you might be unfortunately with the teachers that would give you a -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did they treat the girls the same as the boys in that respect?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, I think so, yes. "cos you see, we had men teachers as well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 What things in particular would you be liable to be punished for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Most probably talking in school, that'd be a very bad thing, talking. Yes, in the class, yo
u'd either be put right at the back of the class or brought right to the front where she could see you. Then again you see I was left handed in a lot of things. I think perhaps I may have been slightly punished to try and use my right hand more. But I thi
nk they did try to do that in a lot at one time. Tried to make you write and do things with the right hand.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did your parents show an interest in your schoolwork?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes I think so, we never had any homework, can't remember we had homework in those days, I don't think we did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Would they ask you questions about what you'd done at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Well I suppose they did but - nothing very definite about it. I mean, if there was anything wrong you would - we - you would come home and tell, see, say what happened at school. You went and you came home all right and that was all that mattered I think.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did they ever visit the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, during times when you had to have examinations. Always had your parents go up with you then on that day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Why?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well examined for your teeth - or your - medical examinations yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 The parents came along too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, the parents used to be asked to come with you know - be there at such and such time which of course a lot of parents didn't go.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did your parents go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. I think my mother used to go.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Why was this, so the doctor could say something to her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, if you got - yes. And they'd - what was I going to say - hm, clean forgotten
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 But your mother would go along with you at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Oh yes, they asked if she would go.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did your parents ever meet the teachers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, there wasn't any special time I think, we did have }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6245793\charrsid12473461 plays}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461  but I can't remember ever, you know - being in those plays. I was - did go in a play once but - I can' remember what happened about it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did the other children in the school mostly come from the same sort of home as yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, I think they did, yes, all local children. They didn't come from far.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Were there any very poor children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 I can't remember them being very poor.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 They were mostly the same sort of homes as you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Yes. Of course some of them were very poorly dressed so of course you just think well they must be poor then, you see, you always thought that when you saw a person badly dressed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did the teachers single out some children for different treatment?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Yes. You always saw there was a certain amount of favouritism.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Which children would usually be the favourites?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well I suppos
e a child that - built herself up to the teacher for that, see, she'd be the type of child that would be - to - be - look well in the teacher's eyes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 So you think it would be mostly to do with the child herself, not her parents or anything?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No,
 nothing to do with the parents, no, with the child, yes. I suppose a teacher would take a dislike which is quite normal isn't it - a liking to anybody.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did teachers particularly single out a better off child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, I don't think so. I don't think that really was the case.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Were there any gangs or groups in the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, I think you seemed to, you know, gang up with the certain type.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Were there any children who were always being left out of things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, there was - yes, ther
e were quite a few that weren't - anybody take notice of. Either because they - they weren't very clever or - you know - there was nothing exciting about them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 That sounds sad, I picture them standing miserably in the playground.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, you saw th
at quite a lot one child standing alone and if you were shy, you see, was another one that's very forward is here there and everywhere.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 With you it would help being one of the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, I was very shy. I never said much. I was very - you know, shy and in coming forward.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did you go to just that one school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, you went to one school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Until you left?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Until I left.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 How old were you when you left?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Fourteen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Could you have stayed on any longer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 I don't k
now if you could have stopped on until you were fifteen. In those days. I suppose I could have passed and gone to a higher school, I think that was possible.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Would you have liked to have done that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 I could have done and gone to Camden High Schoo
l I think that was the place where you'd go. No, I'd no desire to stay home - stop at school, I wanted to leave directly I was fourteen. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Because you hadn't enjoyed it very much?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, I wasn't keen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did you go to any part time classes afterwards?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, nothing whatever. No, I didn't go to any - night schools.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Do you regret that at all now?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. Nothing, no, not at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Do you think you benefited from your schooldays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well whatever I've done today I don't think the
y have helped. I've worked with experience - experience have taught - and all I've done is - I've done on my own self and I've - I've done a lot of things and got through, although perhaps I could have done better. I think it's because I was a bit backwar
d and shy that - that helped - didn't help me you see, don't - that doesn't help does it. Although I did make friends.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Do you feel that school helped you in any way, like how to get on with people or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, I - I don't connect school with anything I've done at all. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 While you were at school did you have any part time job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. No. Didn't have anything. I helped clean the house weekends, I had no -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You didn't do anything you could earn a little money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 So you left school in 1916?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. I was very keen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 The war was on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And you went in the munitions factory?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Factory, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Where was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 That was at - the Mother Shipton in - yes, that was a very well known place.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Was that a pub?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No there - yes, Mother Shipton, yes, it was just there. I', just trying to think where -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 It's somewhere in North London isn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, before you go into Camden Town, now what was the -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6245793\charrsid12473461 Mornington}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461  Crescent?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Mornington }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6245793\charrsid12473461 Crescent}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 . Yes, I suppose it would be near enough there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 This was a big munitions factory?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, it was only a small time factory. Specially munitions - for -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 What were they making?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 I suppose it was garments for the soldier you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 It was garments?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well it was still - steel - what they used to wear in front of their hat to protect their eyes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 How did you get that job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 I don't quite know how I got it, whether I went to the Labour Exchange or - but I went with somebody.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 How did you feel about the work, did you like it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes I liked it and of course I was getting money for it.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And you were probably thrilled to be finished with school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 How long did you stay there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 About six months I think. I should think about six months, yes, I was quite thrilled because I was earning a wage and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Can you remember how much you earned?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 I think I had - I don't think it was much more than ten shillings, ten to fifteen shillings.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 For a whole week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. And -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You left after six months?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Why did you stop doing it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well I don't really know the reason why I stopped, it may have been because it was too much for me or I didn't like it in the en
d or it may be that I was put off, the contract might have finished.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 What did you do then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Then I had some - about six months learning dressmaking. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Were you actually working?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, I was working.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 An apprentice?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, that's right. Apprentice.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 How did you get that job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 I think I got that from some sort of a Labour Exchange.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did you enjoy that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, I went with a girlfriend and - I enjoyed doing that, we were sort of the youngest there and we just did 
sewing buttons on and - light things, learning to begin with.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 But you only stayed six months doing the dressmaking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, about six, yes, then I gave up. I had to give up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Why did you give it up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well because me mother was ill then so I -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 What did you do then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Helped to keep house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 So that really takes us up to about the end of the war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 The war - '18.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You were at home keeping house?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. 'Cos we had all the war - the rest of the war two years after and 
after I left school which was - pretty gruesome. Pretty gruesome that part was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 What jobs have you done since then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well - I was home - then all that time and work - oh well lot of things I could say what I've done, you know. When there's some t
rouble in the family I sort of had to be there - I've been there to help out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You said that when you stopped work and }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6245793\charrsid12473461 stayed}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461  at home to keep house your father actual paid you a wage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Yes, he paid us a wage.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 It was twenty-five shillings you said?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Twenty-five. Every Saturday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 He reckoned that although you were at home and you couldn't go out to work you ought to have your own money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Yes. He - he paid us for what we did and he thought he was doing the right thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Out of that you'd boy your own ...?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
All our things, stockings and all the things we needed. But on special occasions if we wanted any - a big article, we'd ask him for it, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And you paid for your own entertainment?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, whatever we wished to do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 When you were keeping house like that, if you got your work done could you go out if you wanted to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. If wanted to, we tried to work it between us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Since the first world war have you actually done any paid jobs for other people, worked for an employer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 What, from then 'til -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Since the first world war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 'Til now? Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Have you been to a lot of places?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well - I did - I went in a - another factory and did, well small shop it was and made - dressing
 gowns, for a short time. I did that part time. And then I stopped there a little while and - 'cos I was here and looking after Peggy and Bobby at the time, I - was here for four or five years when Bobby was a baby. Well then when the insurance stamps sta
rted to come that I would - if I had insurance stamps I would give you a pension I hadn't got anything up 'til then so I decided to go out to work. So I started about eighteen months after the stamps started and I bought all those back stamps up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 That was what decided you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Yes, decided, yes. That I wanted the stamps otherwise I - I wouldn't have had anything when I get older so then I went to - into a factory and I was there for twelve years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Doing what?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Making - it was in a room, making fridge, motors of the fridges. I was an insulator.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Why did you stop doing that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well I gave that - had to stop and look after my brother's house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And you stayed with him quite a long time didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Well I was there - I gave it up before I was time to give up for my pension. And I finished buying the stamps while I was home.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Because you can always buy them yourself can't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, I did, yes, self-employed. So I was there - what would I be - I was there ten years - I was there I suppose -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Looking after your brother this is?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, seven years I suppose.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Would you have preferred to have done anything else particular in life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. No, I don't think so. No, I didn't hanker after anything. I always wanted to go out to business when I was home. I was -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 When you were looking after the house at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, always a desire to get away from it but -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You worked twelve years in a factory, did you serve an apprenticeship or do any training for that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Well you kind of did have to do it for so long then you were put on a bonus. But you sort of weren't - I don't suppose you were trained, you just had to get up to a certain - before you could go - join the bonus so you could join the other girls 
that took the full - full wage.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 When you were doing that did you belong to any trade union?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, I didn't belong to the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6245793\charrsid12473461 trade union}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 , it wasn't very strong in that company so I never belonged to it, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did you feel that the employers and the workers had the same interests or were they out for different things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Well they was all out for different things but I think the majority would have been content to carry on and not strike because it meant such a - such a - a big draw - back to them for many weeks to come if they hadn't been working.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Do you think the employers were all out for themselves or for the workers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, I think the employers were very good really, they were very good to the workers. They seemed to meet them halfway
 always and - with regards to tea breaks and - and to help them if it was possible if anything happened in the family, they all seemed to you know, come forward and - in that firm they did, they were very good.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 But you felt there were different interests amongst the workers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Well there was really. Yes, well I suppose, everybody had the feeling that - if you - they were going to get a rise you would get it even if you didn't want to - wouldn't join in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Before 1918 some people say there was a great division between trained craftsmen and other workers, do you feel that was true?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Well I think so, there was a difference. Because the trained worker was more employed than the unskilled wasn't he. The unskilled didn't stand a lot of - when thin
gs were slack they went. As a skilled man seemed to be able always although they didn't do so well when they were slack did they.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Would you say that full time work, when you worked in }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6245793\charrsid12473461 munitions}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461  factory or in the dressmaking, would you say that this full time work changed your general attitude to life in any way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Yes, I think so, yes. Oh greatly. Mixing with different class of people, you mix with so many different ones you see. Dressmaking people and people you would get in a factory are totally
 different really. Although of course that has improved a lot, factory workers, at one time they were thought at - very poor people weren't they, they'd no education you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 So when you left school and were doing this when the war was on brought you 
into contact with a lot of people, sort of people you hadn't met before?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
No, and they would be older than me. And then of course it would be more of a novelty. But I do think that the unskilled person would feel - not feel so sure of himself would th
ey, which there again of course education comes in and - sort of training doesn't it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You continued to live at home when you left school when you were working in the factory?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Oh yes, home all the time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did starting this full time work change your relationship with your parents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. No, I don't think so, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did you have a lot of new freedom?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, I think it still went on the same, went - went out a bit more, went dancing but always had that restriction that, you know, I 
didn't want to be out too late at night. I think it was sort of born in you, you just didn't want to stop out late although you daren't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You could now go dancing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And I - yes, could go dancing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did it change your relationship with your brother and sisters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
No, no, we all sort of worked in together, they'd wait up for one another if we were late coming in but of course my father never did like you staying out late at night, it was against his rule really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Now that you were working did you spend Sunday any differently?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well I'd met friends.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did you still go to Sunday school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, no, didn't go to Sunday school after - after a time, I began to grow up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You still spent your Sundays more or less the same?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Just walking, yes. Spent - walking in the evenings. But - practically every evening I went for a walk.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did you ever take any interest in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You never really take an interest in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did you vote in a general election before 1919 - you couldn't have could you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
No, perhaps into their own hands a bit in those days. But today of course - there's such a lot of difference to it isn't there. All cars running round and - those days they were just on foot weren't they and -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Would it be the same policeman most of the time round the area?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 I suppose they were, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did you feel he was a sort of figure in the neighbourhood?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well - well I suppose he was a safeguard, he was safe when he was around sort
 of thing, felt - policeman was going around it was sort of something to - be thankful for.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Was your home rented - it was rented from the railway wasn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 So your landlord was really the railway company?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 The railway company. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did you see somebody, did one particular person come to collect the rent?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, only used to have an agent come regular every week and collect the money. We never saw - anybody else.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 What did you feel about the railway company as a landlord?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Oh, very poor. Yes, they never did a - anything. Never did anything to any of their property of what I know of. I know they never did anything to ours at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did you feel that they wouldn't help you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 They just neglected it and let it go.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 They left you to do anything that needed doing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Do you remember ever feeling that your parents had to struggle to make ends meet.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, I don't think I ever had that feeling.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 When when the children were small?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. No I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 There must have been times where your father was ill and the business wasn't going too good?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well - well I think he always somebody that would take over, he had - two or three men that worked for him and - he got one that was 
very reliable person that he left there because he's away from business quite a lot when he went to auction sale, which he had to go to buy the material to sell.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Can you ever remember periods when the business wasn't doing too well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well no, no,
 I wouldn't remember anything like that. I know in the war of course it did do better. I can remember right, in 1914-1918 war. But - the material - secondhand material of course was well wanted then. But after that time - people didn't want second hand ma
t
erial, they began to want all new stuff. And it gradually went down, secondhand material. But of course it was a great demand at one time for secondhand material because - they repaired a place it was always secondhand material they put in and bodged it. 
They didn't make a thorough job not like today, they just go and buy new material and everything that is on the market. 'Cos there is so much now, there's a variety.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 So you never needed help from anybody?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Was there anybody in your district that was generally disapproved of?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, there were a few, yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 A few people or a few families?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 I say a few families, yes, that - did create and cause a disturbance. Fighting. And perhaps - drinking. They -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Can you remember anybody like that being made to leave the district?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, I can't - don't think they was ever made to leave the district. No, I don't think ever -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 How }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6245793\charrsid12473461 would}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
 the people in the neighbourhood show their disapproval of them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well yes, they woul
d be very whatsname against anything like that, they just wouldn't speak to people you know. They were just shunned. And - don't think they would cover it up.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Can you remember what time your father got home from work in the evenings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well - summer evenings, he'd work on his allotment until - beginning to get dusk you see, while he could he see. Now -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 He would come home from the yard?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Well that's where his allotment was at his place of work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 How long would he go on actually working?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Until - working - his actual working day. Well I suppose they'd finish somewhere around about six o'clock at night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And then he'd go on to the allotment?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, and when the man had gone home and he would go round to his allotment ju
st round the back and - carry on there until - well I suppose, the dusk - in these day it - it seemed to - the evenings seemed to be longer, light - I mean the light held out longer. I can remember, you know, going the - over the Parliament Hill fields an
d playing tennis until - nine o'clock. Or else it's because we went to bed earlier in those days that it may feel that it was -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Can you remember going to bed in the light?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Oh no, we never - not in - half past ten was our usual time for bed. I suppose everybody, you know, going now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And in summer it's often light at half past ten isn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Oh yes. Yes, it's - right in the middle of summer it is isn't it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 So he'd work on the allotment until it was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6245793\charrsid12473461 dusk}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Well I suppose it -
 perhaps it'd be about eight thirty most probably when he come home in the evening and then he'd have a wash. And then he'd just go - have a drink then, go to bed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 What about his meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well - no, he had a meal when he come back after that about 
half past nine to ten he had a supper which I think country people always do that as a rule don't they, have a - a late meal, late supper, they used to do in the country.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 So he'd stay on his allotment 'til about dusk, then he'd come home and have a wash?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Go and have a drink?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And then come home for his supper?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Then he'd come home for his supper. And then he'd go to bed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did he go to any clubs at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. he never belonged to clubs and - he didn't - 
betting - he never did any betting of any sort. No, he was - just worked, had his pleasure in the - his garden and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 So he didn't go to any clubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, no, he never belonged to any clubs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did he go regularly to one pub?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Yes, he always went to the same - pub.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did your mother go too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
No, not very often. Maybe the weekend - she would go. Saturday evening, they would go shopping Saturday evening down - a kind of a market place we had and they' go down round that there 'til a
bout ten a - in the evening 'cos the shops used to be open then until - I suppose eleven or twelve at night, eleven or twelve they were open.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 What sort of shops?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 All the shops - market. Yes, fruit shops and that - all stalls you see and they'd m
ost probably buy fruit and - all that was going. But I don't think she went many evenings with him to the - she may have gone over after he'd been and gone a short while after we was in bed. She may have gone over then for half an hour. Yes, after we was 
in bed she may have slipped out. And I think - which I think she did do but of course I'm not sure because we'd all be in bed and - she would go when we was - there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Have you any idea how long the two of them might spend in the pub?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well they wo
uld close wouldn't they. I don't quite know what time they close but they always used to come home about ten o'clock. So it would only be a short while.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 She would go in and have a drink, she wouldn't just go to fetch him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 She'd go in and have a drink, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Do you know what she would drink?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well I think it would mostly be - most probably be a - a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6245793\charrsid12473461 Guinness}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461  beer, it wouldn't be - or my father would drink - ale. Ale. But he never had short drinks. Don't think they ever had short drinks. No, I don't think they practiced in that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did your father take part in any sport at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, no, he didn't take part in any sport, not as far as I know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did he ever go to the races?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. Oh he was very interested in special days of the racing. He sort of, you know was very - excited those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 But you said before he didn't bet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. No, it wasn't a habit.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 He would just talk about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, he would just talk about, it, yes, on these special days. Which of course if yo
u go to a public house naturally you get in with that conversation don't you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did your mother or father ever belong to any savings clubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. No. No. No, I know what you mean, no, I don't think they did. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Before you left school, when you were children at home, do you remember has you go on with your brothers and sisters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Oh }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6245793\charrsid12473461 well}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
 - yes, we all sort of seemed to - fall in with one another and - just automatically, you know, you - you sort of - you're there and you just - all fall in a
nd do your jobs and - and, you know, we seemed to - I don't know what else - there's anything outstanding about that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And there was always something to do, you all had these jobs?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well yes, I suppose - yes - I -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Was there any one of the family that you were particularly close to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
No, I don't think so, no, don't think so. We was all much around but the same age, there wasn't a great difference between any of us so I suppose that's why we all - like all in one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Which is nice really isn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Well it is, yes. Oh yes. I think it makes a lot of difference - that. Well I think if there's a big gap I think the older child is either - had a lot to do or she thinks she's a little bit more superior than the other one. But if you're ro
und about the same age I just don't think that enters your mind, you just -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Who did you play with as children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 I think myself we did play with our schoolfriends. But we didn't go any distance to play with them, it was either just be outside our 
own locality.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did you play with the neighbours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Well - well I think it was mostly children that we'd met at school we may go out to meet or play with. And of course when you went to Sunday school you made one or two friends there and - well come
 time well you perhaps would make a - arrangements to go out with them in an evening.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Where would you play when you went out like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well - I suppose around the streets I suppose or we had the Parliament Hill fields where you - you'd go - we 
didn't go far away on our own, not until we got to a certain age. And we had a circus, used to go into there a lot. -Like a circus. Seats and - flowers and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 A circular garden?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Cir - yes, we used to call it a circus. It was called - }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6245793\charrsid12473461 Lissimore}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461  Circus. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 That was just flowers and seats?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Just flowers and that and of course you couldn't do - you had to behave yourself if you went in there. But - I don't recall a lot of children playing out in the street although there was plenty round.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did you have a yard you could play in?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 We only had a very small yard.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Were you allowed to play with anyone you liked?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Oh yes, yes, we weren't any restriction about that at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Were there any children that your parents discouraged you from playing with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
No, oh no. No. I don't think in those days you - you had a distinction with children at all, you was all sort of much the same. You didn't get all those rough children. Like - you may have done in some districts, such as - w
ell East End of London but - round about where we lived they was all much about the same. Of course our only place we did go to was Parliament Hill fields which was - nearly everybody knows that Hampstead was a - a very vast place. You could just play ove
r there, we used to just play there. Walk over there and play. As we got a little older we played tennis. Most probably - they may have played cricket over there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did you play tennis on a public court?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Public court - grass court.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Apart from the Sunday school did you belong to any other youth things at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Well - we did belong to the Girl Guides when we got to a certain age. I don't suppose you'd be very old. Well I suppose we'd be about eight wouldn't we - eight. Yes, went and joined the Girl Guides. My eldest sister did and I did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did they have Brownies in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, I don't remember about - I don't think they did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You went straight into the Guides?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 It - straight into the Guides and we used - must have g
one there one night - two nights a week. I can remember - doing a few - learning morse and signaling and a few things, I can just remember but I didn't stay there a great long while I think
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 I'd like to ask you about how you spent your free time when y
ou were at school, in the evenings when you couldn't go out to play did you have any hobbies?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Oh I think we would play perhaps cards if we was all together or - we didn't have a lot of games. I don't think they did have a lot of games in those days, 
I don't think they did. Remember having plenty of cards but - all the variety of games they've got today I don't think they were - no, I think we used to just sit around. Or just play on our own. You sort of - it's surprising what you can play with and no
t have any toys to do it with.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did you have any pets?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Oh we had plenty of - yes, two, three cats and dogs. We had two dogs. Yes, we always seemed to have cats and dogs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6245793\charrsid12473461 Did any of the family, did you, collect anything?}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well, yes, we c
ollected things that we were told to at school. Such as - perhaps going out in botany and collecting flowers and pressing them in a book. That was all to do with the school. But it was more or less a hobby as well because - I don't think we had to do anyt
hing in those days, like - I don't think we had homework we never had any homework. I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 So you think the teacher more or less suggested this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Suggested it. Must have done, I mean, and we take them. And they would say well, see 
how many you can get. And then we'd press them all in the book and take them - all little things like that that perhaps, you know, it didn't cost any money to do, it was all - interesting.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Can you remember collecting anything else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, I don't think so. I don't think we collected anything else.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did you ever do any gardening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6245793\charrsid12473461 
No, we never had a garden you see, it was mostly just the allotment that was sort of interest if we went up there was to pick any fruit that was around.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 When you went up there did you ever do any planting or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, we never did any, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Would you help your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, we might watch him and - he would tell us all about it, you know, what he'd grown and proudly give it to us to take home
 for our meal the next day which we always had our own vegetables.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 How big would the allotment be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Oh was quite a big place. What could I say - oh this'd be about thirty square fee something like that.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Twice the size of this room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Yes, it'd be quite a long piece, it run right along by the - the railway it did, and the back of his works.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 So it was a pretty big allotment?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Oh yes, it was. He had all sorts of things there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did you ever go fishing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, never went fishing, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did your father go fishing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. No, he was very - very keen on shooting.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 When would he do his shooting?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well he - we had a - there was a pond in this place where he had his works and he used to have wild ducks flying and
 he shot them. But he would take - put some - I don't know what else are - are they a - yes, are they - they come from - a seed or do they come from - an eel - well the baby ones, he'd put them in and they would grow and he would catch 'em and }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6245793\charrsid12473461 bring}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461  'em home and we'd cook 'em for lunch - dinner.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You went for walks?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Yes, you - I think that practically the whole time we had free we just walked about and - you notice what other people was doing I suppose which took our attention and kept us occupied.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You used to go for quite long walks didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did you ever bicycle?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, I didn't have a bicycle. I think - yes, I think my eldest sister had a bicycle but I never went.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 There was quite a craze for bicycling wasn't there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, but - well wasn't many cars on the road those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 It was a good way of getting around wasn't it?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 About - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Do you remember your sisters having special clothes for bicycling?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, we just - never had anything special f
or anything. Just wear what you'd have. It wouldn't be a long way you'd go, sort of only round and round the - the - roads where you lived, back turnings.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 When you went for walks, you would often go with your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, that was mostly on a Sunday he would go for walk over the - Parliament Hills, otherwise he never went. Well there wasn't much time.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Other times when you went for walks who would you go with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Perhaps with a girl friend. We all went different phase. But we did play tennis together.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And there'd always be someone to go for a walk with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did you take part in any sports apart from the tennis?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, I played tennis, only just ordinary sports day sports at school and - school treats, we had school tr
eat once a year and then we belonged to Sunday school and they always had a - school treat once a year. And I suppose they must have had some sort of - recreational in the - in the rooms at the Sunday club.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You mentioned cricket?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, my brother used to play cricket, we used to play cricket.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You'd all play?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Yes. If you went away to the country we used to play in the evenings. We didn't do anything else. It's surprising how - how your time you can fill in with not doing anything }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid81240\charrsid12473461 particularly.}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461  No television and nom - no wireless. We did have a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6245793\charrsid12473461 gramophone}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
 which was just a - a horn one. That was the only amusement we had in the house. We did have a piano but nobody was very good at playing, we used to amuse ourself playing - five fingers, t
hat's all. But we did have the opportunity to have learnt if we wanted to. But we weren't very musical I don't think. I think my father was very fond of music, he liked to listen to the music.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did you ever go to the theatre?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, I don't think w
e went to theatres. Not until I was older. As a child we never went to the theatre. No. We may have gone to the cinema. Yes, they used to have a lot of concerts in those days I think. Kind of a concert you know - it wouldn't be like a concert today.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You'd occasionally go to those would you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Would they be held in the evenings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
At Band of Hope I think they used to call them. We're going to the Band of Hope. I don't know really what we did there but I know it used to be called the Band of Hope. Band of Hope.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Something to do with religion?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Yes, I think that was to do with the church, they called it the Band of Hope. I suppose - I remember that but what we did there I don't know. It wasn't very far away, just - quite local, the church.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Sometimes while you were still at school you'd go to the cinema?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 When would you go to the cinema?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well I suppose it would be on a Saturday if we ever went, it wouldn't be in the evening.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Saturday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Morning or afternoon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Oh, it'd be in the afternoon, late afternoon, we wouldn't go late evening I don't think. I don't think they kept }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid81240\charrsid12473461 open}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461  very late, I can't remember about that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Who would you go to the cinema with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Oh most probably would be a girlfriend we'd go.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 This was while you were still at school?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did your parents give you any pocket money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. We had plenty of pocket money.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 While you were at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. We had just - well - we had relatives round t
hat would give you a ha'penny, had relatives. Or a penny. And you mostly divided that penny up to last - twice. But we didn't have a lot of sweets.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did your parents give you any bit of money regularly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, we - no we never had anything regular, no. Used to have - we always sort of -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Just people gave you odd bits?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, that's right, always seemed to have a few sweets given to us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 So it wasn't until you left school that you had any regular money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, not until we left school, no. Not that I - not what you could call real pocket money.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 If someone did give you some money you said you'd spend it on sweets?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, it would be spent on sweets or if my mother did happen to give us any money. If we did anything he would give 
you something, always gave you something.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Nobody outside the home ever helped your mother to look after it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, no, I don't remember anybody coming in helping, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 What about when she was ill?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 There again I don't remember anybody coming in but - no, I can't remember any of her sisters coming in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Later on when she was ill you looked after her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 When you were smaller, when she was having a baby maybe, who would come in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 I can remember a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6245793\charrsid12473461 midwife}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461  coming in and - most probably we would have a - perhaps an auntie come in to perhaps just see to us but - I can't remember, you know. I can't - remember how the meals went about that }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid81240\charrsid12473461 time.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461  There's nothing sort of definite I could think of that would - think that we ha
d somebody to come and do all I think perhaps my father may have been very capable man and - could easy adapt himself to anything to do without making any - any bother about it. But most probably we all did jobs for - you wouldn't think anything of it bec
ause it comes normal to you when you're brought up like that.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did your parents have any relatives living nearby?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Oh yes. My mother's people lived in London.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 She came from there of course didn't she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. My father's parents - they didn't, they lived -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 So it was your mother's relatives who lived nearby?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Mostly my mother's relatives but my father's relatives did - did call and see us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 How much do you think your mother saw of her relatives?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Oh quite often. Because it was only just a few yards away they lived - all -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Would she call on them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Without any previous arrangement?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Oh yes, yes, they just call on one another. And we would just call on them just the same.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You'd call on each other at your own houses?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Just call in without any - invitation.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did your parents have friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Well - I don't think they made any special friends that, you know, came in regular. No, we weren't - not like you do see today, people have parties don't they and have friends in. I don't think we }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid81240\charrsid12473461 ever}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461  did that. I don't think, my father and mother had friends in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You don't think they had any special friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 \{ILLEGIBLE\}
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did your mother have any friends of her own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. Don't 
think so. They always - a family, they always seemed to be - that was enough, their family to visit them and - they didn't need friends.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did you think your father had any special friends at the pub or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. No. Only his - normal - good evening and that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6245793\charrsid12473461 Acquaintances}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, just acquaintances.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You can't remember friends ever being invited into the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. No. There wasn't a lot of time for - for that because my father's working most of the time. He wouldn
't have a lot of time to entertain I don't - nor would my mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Would any of the neighbours call in casually without an invitation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, no, they never came in, no. We seemed to be more spread apart than - houses there, you know, didn't seem to
 be on top of one another like the small houses are here, you can look out the back and - you know, and talk to people. Oh we always }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6245793\charrsid12473461 spoke}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461  to people if you was near and they spoke to us but we never made any friends.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 People often tell us that they mad
e their own amusements in those days, what do you think your parents did when they were together with neighbours or relatives?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well I suppose they would talk about general affairs, I can't imagine 'em - anything else.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Do you think they might have made some music?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. No. No, I don't think they did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Would they have played any games?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Card games?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, no, we - never played cards.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You think they'd just talk?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 They would just talk, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did your parents ever go into the neighbours houses to visit them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, I don't think they did. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Many people divide society into different social classes or groups.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 In that time before 1918, did you think of some people belonging to one class and some people belonging to another?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Well - of course there was the very poor people but - a suppose you - there were people you thought were better off than yourself. I don't know why - why you thought that, way they dressed or way they lived or in what property they lived.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 How many classes would you say there were then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well I only think there was - round our - few classes. The very poor people or the middle class person.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You mean around where you were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. But the - the other 
class well - the upper class - you didn't come in - connection with them at all, unless you went into another district. They seemed to be like that, you know, all kept their own - what was the property I suppose makes a lot of difference and that. }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6245793\charrsid12473461 Different - say - where would the property be expensive - oh I suppose you could say perhaps Golders Green. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Or }{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6245793\charrsid12473461 Hampstead}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
 you'd think was a - bit different to where you lived. But you see again where we lived there wasn't poverty, not what you call real poverty. No
t like in the - East End of London where you could see children running around without anything on their feet, no clothing much on and hanging around outside their doors }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6245793\charrsid12473461 unkempt}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 . But - I don't remember seeing much of that round our way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Which class or group would you say you belonged to yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Well I'd say the middle class. I would say there only - they was only - in my opinion, there was only three classed. The poor, middle class and the - well - what you call the higher people. Society peopl
e or - no - the gentry - gentile. Yes, the gentry, yes, I think they were called that in those days, the gentry. The gentry. And I think they did really, you know, look up to them. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 If your family saw itself as belonging to the middle class what other sort of people would you think were in that class as well?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well - I suppose mostly }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6245793\charrsid12473461 trades people}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461  and - }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6245793\charrsid12473461 trades people}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461  and - people that had their own businesses I suppose.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Like your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Who was able to have just that little more than - the average.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 What sort of people would you say belonged to the poorer class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Well the labourer I should say, the man and the dustman and people like that in those days, of course the - they were badly poor - paid weren't they. And they did appear to be poorer, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You mean by the look of them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
By the - yes, and by the - the way they went about, you know, they had a lot of children, they always seemed to have - six and eight children. But they did appear to be very poor. But you }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6245793\charrsid12473461 
classed}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
 'em as that the dustmen and - as being poor, those days. They - well, I don't think it's gone that much different today has it? I know they do get good wages but they still - it still is that job isn't it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 What sort of people would you have thought of as belonging to the gentry?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Well - I don't quite know, I suppose you would people that didn't have to go to work but was at home. You know, people that were retired, not retired, but - they didn't seem to have to work like the other people. Not the daily work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 But they had money to live on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Yes. And I suppose you would say even you say a bank clerk you would think was - a little better than yourself. I don't know why, 'cos they were dressed better.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did they have to work every day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, they had to work every day but they was - wouldn't come like the gentry.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Where would you have thought some of them would fit in, like a policeman?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well I would say he would fit in the middle class.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 What about someone like, someone who worked in someone else's shop?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Well - no, I would still think he - he was more or less, like in the middle class. It was just those - poorly paid jobs such as the - the labourer and - did all and they looked it.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 What about someone like a doctor?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Yes, well - you - you - everyone has a different opinion about that. I always thought you know they were - something above everybody else which of course they are Yes. And of course we did have a private doctor which - you know
 - makes a heap of difference to the - people that was on the panel, they didn't get treated all that well did they on the panel in those days. Very poor.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You feel that the doctor was a bit above you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, I would say, yes. 'Cos there again you see, he dressed that part. Our doctor did - morning dress. Topper - high hat.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Would you say a lot depended on the way a person dressed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well I think it did in those - yes, I think it did, yes, in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Can you remember being brought up to treat people of one sort differently from another?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. No, I don't think we was. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Were you ever told to curtsey to anybody?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 To show respect in any way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Show respect, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 How would you show respect?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well - we weren't expected to say much those days, child supposed to stand }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid81240\charrsid12473461 
back,}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461  and listen. And not interrupt, yes, and not interrupt when grown ups were speaking.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Would that apply to any grown ups, not matter who they were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Oh yes. You never - you n
ever interrupted while grown ups were speaking. We just was there and you didn't - didn't speak. Not in our family.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Were there any people that your parents asked you particularly to show respect to
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. My mother used to say, well, your aunties c
oming today - that'd be my father's sister which - she came up from - the North. She'd come over for the day and see us and of course we thought as we have to be very good and polite and - she bring some cakes and we thought that was quite wonderful, and 
we looked toward to coming so I think by that we couldn't have had a lot of visitors 'cos we - we used to always stand and - didn't say much. We weren't a family to do a lot of talking, we were rather quiet.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Was there anybody you called sir or madam?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, it'd only be anybody at school I think. You sort of respected people at school the teachers and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Would you call them sir?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, yes, you would think that they had to be called sir and - the headmaster.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 What would you call the woman teacher?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Well I suppose you would just say yes, teacher, I don't think she would say - I don't think you would - address her any other way unless it was by her name.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Do you remember in particular showing respect to your parents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. No. No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 If they went into a shop?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Oh I don't think they would only address 'em as - by their name. Yes. Yes. Yes. I think by saying - they respected them that way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Can you remember who were considered the most important people in the district?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Well I suppose - well say doctor and a man that - I'm just trying to think of the - perhaps a bank manager you'd say or man that held a very high position - fairly high position such as a man that - what is he that you go to - to - 
one of those, what do they call them? Yes, solicitor. Those type of people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Would they be known to }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid81240\charrsid12473461 everybody}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, they would be known to most people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And people would know who they were when they saw them in the street?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 N
o. No. No. The doctor'd be the only one that I could remember as being - besides the schoolmaster, he always seems to be - a main - one of the main people in - in childhood I think. Headmistress.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Why do you think people like that were considered important?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 I don't know, they seemed to be - to be the had of - of a lot of things don't they.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Why do you think that people looked up to them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well they had so much to do with so many people don't they, you know, a lot of people depend on them.
 That's, I think, the main thing. So many people depend on the things they can do for them. Because they are just clever than you are yourself, they know more.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Do you think it was because they knew so much?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, it's because you think they know 
so much that you - you just think they are a lot better than what you are and I think that is with a - a lot of people, if you're clever you - that you are inclined to think that they are - sort of rely on them can't you, or you think you - you can rely o
n them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 What about shopkeepers locally, who did they make friends and associate with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Well - I don't - I don't think that they were - I can't remember them being - associate with anybody. Anybody in particular. They all had their own - places, I suppose, they were interested in. Church.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 What about the clergy themselves, did they associate with anybody in particular?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, not unless you specially went out for their help.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Would the teachers associate with anyone in particular?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, I don't think so. I }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid81240\charrsid12473461 don\rquote t}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461  think they would - I don't think they did so much those days that - they do today. A teacher when she'd finished her - time that teaching during the day that was the finish. That was all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You mean she went home then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 She went home. Never heard of knew of her.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did you know where your teacher lived?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. No, I didn't know anything, no, I didn't know anything of her particular -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Would you know who her friends were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. Today they do, they seem to kn
ow more or less their - their life a lot more once they've left school you know, where they belong, where they live but I can't remember anything whatever about the teachers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 What sort of people locally would you say were the people who went to church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
There was always a certain type that went to church. We were really - we used to think they were just - trying to be a little better than anybody else, don't know \{ILLEGIBLE\}. But you used to see them, the regular ones, go to church every Sunday, u
sed to go round past us. But - I don't know why you thought they were any better than what you were.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Was there any difference locally between church and chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No, we only just had the one church, we did have another church which was rather }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid81240\charrsid12473461 high.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did a particular sort of people go there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, a different type of people went to high church. I -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 What sort of people went to the high church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 I don't know, I didn't have much to do with those type of people, they lived right a - 
away from us, you see, you didn't come in connection with those people did you as a child - you - they kept - always seemed to keep to their way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You mean the people that went to high}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid81240\charrsid12473461  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Were they a better off people or poorer people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
No, I don't think any better off. I used to like to go to the high church. I went a few times, I don't know whether it was the novelty of it or - it was more }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid81240\charrsid12473461 interesting. Candles and the in}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 cense. Yes, I rather liked it. I thought it was something that drew you more. Sort of -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 You feel that there was a particular type of person that went to high church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 But you can't put a name to it?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Where you lived did all the people in the working class or the poorer classes have
 the same standard of living or would you say there were different groups?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 No. I - I think - all seemed to be on the same group of the way they lived.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 So as far as you were concerned you would say all the poorer class people were all very much the same?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 That's it, they were more or less the same. Didn't have a lot of - food I suppose to eat, I mean, they }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid81240\charrsid12473461 must}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461  have had very little.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Is that characteristic of a family in the poorer classes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, they didn't get a lot to eat. Well it
 would be plain food, bread and - bread and butter would be main - their main diet I suppose. And - cheap meat.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 What else would be noticeable about a family like that can you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Well they all lived more lived in together more you know, th
ey sort of was never - regards to their home life. As you know, a lot of them didn't have bathrooms so they just wash in the same room as where other people were which to me that did seem wrong.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 As a child that seemed wrong to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And as a child did you think that was a mark of being very poor?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Yes, I thought it was - it wouldn't be - it wasn't right that should - just stand and wash in front of other people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid81240\charrsid12473461 Within}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461  the poorer classes were some families thought of as ro
ugh and others as respectable?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Yes. You could -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 So you could have respectable poor people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Yes, you could tell the difference of the very poor, of a mother and father taking their - their children out although they were poor their beh
aviour was very good and they behaved the children did. And then there was again the poor that didn't care - way they went on. They were left to roam around the best way they could.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Do you remember a distinction of this kind between labourers and craftsmen?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Well, yes, you always classed it as that. You sort of - anybody with a good job and you thought had got a good - nice home and dressed well you would sort of class them as - being a lot better than the real poor.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did you feel that craftsmen were a cut above labourers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 
Yes. As I say, manager or - a foreman you thought was a lot better. I would have thought was a lot better than - the ordinary - what shall I say - the ordinary people who were working in a factory.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Was it considered something of value to have a craft or a trade?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Oh yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Was a carpenter more or less respectable than a labourer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes. Yes, you would think so, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 More respectable?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 'Cos his job was - those days he - he was a craftsman.
 It was perfect although it was done - perhaps took a long while to do it - he was a thorough craftsman. And he - you know - and he whatsnamed his job because those days there was a lot of unemployment so -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did your mother and father have the same attitude to people in the different classes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Oh yes, I don't think they - looked down on anybody.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Did they have the same attitude as each other, did they both behave in the same was
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Oh yes, yes, I think they did, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 And you feel that they also behaved in the same way to different people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Yes, I think - they would feel more or less sorry for them than - and - anything else.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 Do you think your mother saw herself as belonging to a particular class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6908668 OH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 She may have done. Her won father was a - quite a - self made man and - a good home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2960679 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3541791\charrsid12473461 He was self employed wasn't he?
\par }}